{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}
{% trans_default_domain 'FOSUserBundle' %}
{% include 'header.html.twig' %}
<section>
  {% include 'aside.html.twig' %}
  <div class="container">
    <section class="contenue--dashboard">
      <article class="show--desc">
        <p class="main-text-dashboard">Bonjour <span>{{app.user.username}} {{app.user.firstname}}</span> et bienvenue sur <span>Workplace</span></p>
        <p class="text--dashboard">
          Sed tamen haec cum ita tutius observentur, quidam vigore artuum inminuto rogati ad nuptias ubi aurum dextris manibus cavatis offertur, inpigre vel usque Spoletium pergunt. haec nobilium sunt instituta.
